{"tid":2508682,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 母親節驚喜","createTime":"2021-04-29T02:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T13:44:21.000Z","uid":281492,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b9a50c284ca0cd0acb1ee38b40b69903e7266d18","tid":2508682,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:50:47.000Z","msg":"今年母親節嘅禮物已經買咗<br />\n但係已經肛囊才盡<br />\n諗唔到點送出去<br />\n所以開個po同大家分享下<br />\n順便向大家取經<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家有啲好好笑但唔過分嘅建議<br />\n我老母都幾玩得下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前試過：<br />\n<br />\n1、前年將條港女頸鏈連盒擺入微波爐<br />\n呃老母話微波爐好污糟<br />\n佢拎毛巾去抹嗰陣就發現咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2、上年老母胃唔舒服入院<br />\n佢係喺母親節前幾日入院嘅<br />\n好擔心自己要一個人喺醫院度過母親節<br />\n不過佢好彩，嗰日晏晝5點走得<br />\n我將金戒指擺喺區議員派嘅假花入面<br />\n扮無乜嘢送俾佢<br />\n得條濕鳩珍珠手鏈&amp;一朵假花<br />\n老母話唔緊要，有心就得喇<br />\n我哋等佢擰下擰下自己發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但最後都要我提佢先發現到<br />\n佢笑到痴Q咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個口塞得落成個拳頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆睇到好羨慕嘅時候<br />\n我哋就拎另一隻金戒指出嚟送埋俾佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3ba4c7aebeb2749b9769331cc53e6cbb6f2dc6","tid":2508682,"uid":392196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:52:24.000Z","msg":"幾乖"},{"pid":"729456602f1bd44b38a7ba410f107f920b0229db","tid":2508682,"uid":93096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:52:32.000Z","msg":"施媽幸福..<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c47b490cd288a108ca6114ac765af58a60a5df6","tid":2508682,"uid":281492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da3ba4c7aebeb2749b9769331cc53e6cbb6f2dc6","tid":2508682,"uid":392196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:52:24.000Z","msg":"幾乖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:54:12.000Z","msg":"係孝順，但唔乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcf89dbf397dade3952d7d90d8dc3ccdf4c4d66","tid":2508682,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"729456602f1bd44b38a7ba410f107f920b0229db","tid":2508682,"uid":93096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:52:32.000Z","msg":"施媽幸福..<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:54:23.000Z","msg":"我仲幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e516fdf306f51554a128ab1248fc865fe8bd534","tid":2508682,"uid":108816,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:58:12.000Z","msg":"咁撚有心 <br />\n男人老狗大個都係請老母食餐飯就算啦<br />\n仲要可能同兄弟姐妹夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74497b3da5ce2ee7d90e5246906c29570b32fd30","tid":2508682,"uid":281492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e516fdf306f51554a128ab1248fc865fe8bd534","tid":2508682,"uid":108816,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:58:12.000Z","msg":"咁撚有心 <br />\n男人老狗大個都係請老母食餐飯就算啦<br />\n仲要可能同兄弟姐妹夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"