assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前試過：<br />\n<br />\n1、前年將條港女頸鏈連盒擺入微波爐<br />\n呃老母話微波爐好污糟<br />\n佢拎毛巾去抹嗰陣就發現咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2、上年老母胃唔舒服入院<br />\n佢係喺母親節前幾日入院嘅<br />\n好擔心自己要一個人喺醫院度過母親節<br />\n不過佢好彩，嗰日晏晝5點走得<br />\n我將金戒指擺喺區議員派嘅假花入面<br />\n扮無乜嘢送俾佢<br />\n得條濕鳩珍珠手鏈&amp;一朵假花<br />\n老母話唔緊要，有心就得喇<br />\n我哋等佢擰下擰下自己發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但最後都要我提佢先發現到<br />\n佢笑到痴Q咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個口塞得落成個拳頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆睇到好羨慕嘅時候<br />\n我哋就拎另一隻金戒指出嚟送埋俾佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:16:26.000Z","msg":"八歲就蒸嘢食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7188c38802058cf40c2ce969f6eaa02f52534360","tid":2508682,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"837fc21a5c11a54dbed8efd43ca95d764ea3803b","tid":2508682,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:11:01.000Z","msg":"no 人理me<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:20:55.000Z","msg":"連登仔：<br />\n橋我_<br />\n錢你_<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef8caf3a6a346fe4dd13ec09038cc15bc74017c","tid":2508682,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:22:18.000Z","msg":"講左咩禮物先再幫你諗<img src=\"/assets