/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會蒸一蒸就溶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:23:55.000Z","msg":"佢屈一屈都變形喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6087471f8ab00cf1d500a8b05af1873f7f4f511a","tid":2508682,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc9243044827a17349afc3ccdb8f45476862242d","tid":2508682,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0861ef6dfb05d44c03cabecdc154fc0c1c0e18e5","tid":2508682,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9a50c284ca0cd0acb1ee38b40b69903e7266d18","tid":2508682,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:50:47.000Z","msg":"今年母親節嘅禮物已經買咗<br />\n但係已經肛囊才盡<br />\n諗唔到點送出去<br />\n所以開個po同大家分享下<br />\n順便向大家取經<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家有啲好好笑但唔過分嘅建議<br />\n我老母都幾玩得下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前試過：<br />\n<br />\n1、前年將條港女頸鏈連盒擺入微波爐<br />\n呃老母話微波爐好污糟<br />\n佢拎毛巾去抹嗰陣就發現咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2、上年老母胃唔舒服入院<br />\n佢係喺母親節前幾日入院嘅<br />\n好擔心自己要一個人喺醫院度過母親節<br />\n不過佢好彩，嗰日晏晝5點走得<br />\n我將金戒指擺喺區議員派嘅假花入面<br />\n扮無乜嘢送俾佢<br />\n得條濕鳩珍珠手鏈&amp;一朵假花<br />\n老母話唔緊要，有心就得喇<br />\n我哋等佢擰下擰下自己發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但最後都要我提佢先發現到<br />\n佢笑到痴Q咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個口塞得落成個拳頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆睇到好羨慕嘅時候<br />\n我哋就拎另一隻金戒指出嚟送埋俾佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:16:26.000Z","msg":"八歲就蒸嘢食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:30:54.000Z","msg":"仲要完全冇煮食經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b34a38ec0345de530c246d7b14e646d1c325f0","tid":2508682,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"521a63066349c0a938dcb9d2db0cb27b05a2144e","tid":2508682,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f28bf0ea64d85a7c9418140426d34d3f360f1d6","tid":2508682,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f317208acee94faaa060533e47d2de19a984a87","tid":2508682,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:55:18.000Z","msg":"女人話要家用呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/short.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:56:20.000Z","msg":"=試下唔畀呀, 砍死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif